Class DataProcessService

  • java.lang.Object
    • beans.services.DataProcessService

    DataService, ReplyService

    public abstract class DataProcessService
extends java.lang.Object
    This super class handles the methods that the two sub classes users, these medhods interacts with the Python Web Framework by sending a request to it as well as another medhod that sends JMS messages to the Database Server.
